OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774368667
OL,3,CDozens evacuated from train after
OL,4,Ccarriage catches fire
OL,6,FDozens of passengers were evacuated
OL,7,Ffrom a train in South Devon after it
OL,8,Fcaught fire.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,Ftrain near Newton Abbot after reports
OL,12,Fof smoke and flames at around 2.30pm
OL,13,Fon Sunday 22 March.
OL,15,FFive fire engines, along with crews
OL,16,Ffrom Newton Abbot Fire Station,
OL,17,FTorquay Fire Station, and Middlemoor
OL,18,FFire Station.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
