OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774368667
OL,3,CDozens evacuated from train after
OL,4,Ccarriage catches fire
OL,6,FAround 30 passengers were forced to
OL,7,Fleave the train and safely removed
OL,8,Ffrom the area.
OL,10,FThe fire service said overheating
OL,11,Fbrakes had caused the fire.
OL,13,FA spokesperson from Newton Abbot Fire
OL,14,FStation said: "Upon arrival, Torquay
OL,15,FFire Station was already in attendance
OL,16,Fand making efforts to deal with the
OL,17,Fincident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774368667
OL,3,CDozens evacuated from train after
OL,4,Ccarriage catches fire
OL,6,F"Smoke and flames had been witnessed
OL,7,Fto be issuing from underneath a train
OL,8,Fcarriage whilst passengers were still
OL,9,Faboard.
OL,11,F"Crews quickly established that the
OL,12,Fsource of the heat was due to the
OL,13,Fbrakes overheating. Two firefighters
OL,14,Futlised a hose reel jet in order to
OL,15,Fcool these brakes to safer
OL,16,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
