PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774368667
OL,3,CDozens evacuated from train after
OL,4,Ccarriage catches fire
OL,6,F"Thankfully, a quick response to a
OL,7,Fdynamic situation ensured that the
OL,8,Fincident was resolved in both a safe
OL,9,Fand quick manner, thereby averting a
OL,10,Fmajor incident.
OL,12,F"We would like to thank all the other
OL,13,Fcrews that responded, including
OL,14,FTorquay Fire Station and Middlemoor
OL,15,FFire Station.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
